#. <section class="sutta" id="sn20.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga"
msgstr "1. Similes"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn20.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Dhanuggahasutta"
msgstr "6. The Archers"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.266"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn20.6:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, cattāro daḷhadhammā dhanuggahā susikkhitā katahatthā "
"katūpāsanā catuddisā ṭhitā assu."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose there were four well-trained expert archers with strong "
"bows standing in the four directions."

msgctxt "sn20.6:1.3"
msgid "Atha puriso āgaccheyya:"
msgstr "And a man came along and thought:"

msgctxt "sn20.6:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ imesaṃ catunnaṃ daḷhadhammānaṃ dhanuggahānaṃ susikkhitānaṃ "
"katahatthānaṃ katūpāsanānaṃ catuddisā kaṇḍe khitte appatiṭṭhite pathaviyaṃ "
"gahetvā āharissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When these four well-trained expert archers shoot arrows in four "
"directions, I’ll catch them before they reach the ground, and then I’ll "
"bring them back.’"

msgctxt "sn20.6:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn20.6:1.6"
msgid "‘javano puriso paramena javena samannāgato’ti alaṃvacanāyā”ti?"
msgstr "Are they qualified to be called ‘a speedster, with ultimate speed’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.6:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ekassa cepi, bhante, daḷhadhammassa dhanuggahassa susikkhitassa "
"katahatthassa katūpāsanassa kaṇḍaṃ khittaṃ appatiṭṭhitaṃ pathaviyaṃ gahetvā "
"āhareyya:"
msgstr ""
"“If he could catch an arrow shot by just one well-trained expert archer "
"before it reaches the ground and bring it back,"

msgctxt "sn20.6:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘javano puriso paramena javena samannāgato’ti alaṃvacanāya, ko pana vādo "
"catunnaṃ daḷhadhammānaṃ dhanuggahānaṃ susikkhitānaṃ katahatthānaṃ "
"katūpāsanānan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"he’d be qualified to be called ‘a speedster, with ultimate speed’. How much "
"more so arrows shot by four archers!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.6:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Yathā ca, bhikkhave, tassa purisassa javo, yathā ca candimasūriyānaṃ javo, "
"tato sīghataro."
msgstr "“As fast as that man is, the sun and moon are faster."

#. VAR: () → tāsaṃ devatānaṃ javo) (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn20.6:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yathā ca, bhikkhave, tassa purisassa javo yathā ca candimasūriyānaṃ javo "
"yathā ca yā devatā candimasūriyānaṃ purato dhāvanti tāsaṃ devatānaṃ javo, () "
"tato sīghataraṃ āyusaṅkhārā khīyanti."
msgstr ""
"As fast as that man is, as fast as the sun and moon are, and as fast as the "
"deities that run before the sun and moon are, the waning of the life forces "
"is faster."

msgctxt "sn20.6:3.3"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "sn20.6:3.4"
msgid "‘appamattā viharissāmā’ti."
msgstr "‘We will stay diligent.’"

msgctxt "sn20.6:3.5"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.6:3.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
